1
00:00:00,250 --> 00:00:02,880
Regarding the app's recipes,

2
00:00:02,880 --> 00:00:04,210
allegations of plagiarism
have surfaced.

3
00:00:04,210 --> 00:00:05,630
This has caused a public outcry,

4
00:00:05,750 --> 00:00:06,170
and to everyone

5
00:00:06,170 --> 00:00:07,460
this has caused a great deal of trouble.

6
00:00:07,710 --> 00:00:09,250
I am truly and deeply sorry.

7
00:00:09,630 --> 00:00:11,830
Sorry doesn't cut it.

8
00:00:12,290 --> 00:00:13,830
We've suffered huge losses because of this.

9
00:00:13,830 --> 00:00:15,330
Do you have any idea?

10
00:00:15,420 --> 00:00:17,880
This incident has caused serious delays
to the project's schedule.

11
00:00:17,880 --> 00:00:19,630
And it's created chaos within the company.

12
00:00:19,880 --> 00:00:21,460
But these are just allegations of plagiarism...

13
00:00:21,460 --> 00:00:22,670
Spare me the excuses!

14
00:00:24,130 --> 00:00:26,830
It's your fault
we have to work overtime every day.

15
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:28,460
My kid is waiting for me at home.

16
00:00:28,670 --> 00:00:30,830
The feeling of your family waiting
when you can't come home...

17
00:00:30,830 --> 00:00:32,170
Can you even imagine that?

18
00:00:32,170 --> 00:00:34,330
I'll let it slide for the handsome president's sake.

19
00:00:34,330 --> 00:00:35,330
But you have to make it up to us.

20
00:00:35,630 --> 00:00:37,500
I already
apologized just now.

21
00:00:37,630 --> 00:00:39,540
Listen,
that's not how you make amends.

22
00:00:39,540 --> 00:00:40,960
Don't you even know
how to apologize properly?

23
00:00:41,210 --> 00:00:43,500
Isn't there a bit too much space
between your head and the floor?

24
00:00:43,500 --> 00:00:44,880
The space between my head and the floor...

25
00:00:45,130 --> 00:00:46,960
With all due respect,

26
00:00:47,130 --> 00:00:48,790
it wasn't actually plagiarism.

27
00:00:48,790 --> 00:00:51,210
For something that's just
a baseless rumor,

28
00:00:51,210 --> 00:00:53,670
is it really necessary
to go this far?

29
00:00:53,670 --> 00:00:54,880
How dare you talk back?

30
00:00:55,210 --> 00:00:56,460
Sami...

31
00:00:56,630 --> 00:00:58,790
As an adult...

32
00:00:59,130 --> 00:01:00,670
Fine. You say it's not plagiarism.

33
00:01:01,130 --> 00:01:02,830
Then prove
you didn't do it.

34
00:01:02,830 --> 00:01:03,830
Since you put it that way...

35
00:01:04,130 --> 00:01:05,580
If you would just look
at my recipe notebook,

36
00:01:06,130 --> 00:01:07,710
it would prove that I didn't
plagiarize anything.

37
00:01:08,710 --> 00:01:10,920
What? If you have it,
show it to us now!

38
00:01:11,210 --> 00:01:13,130
The notebook... is gone.
